{"text": "Welcome to the practice of emptiness. In the previous sessions of meditation training we have worked with the breathing body, following the airflow, observing the air, witnessing the presence of air. You can appreciate that air is an invisible element. We shall now shift to meditating on emptiness. Yes, similar to how the air is an invisible element. You can appreciate the shift to working with something that is also not visible, the emptiness, the emptiness, the empty space. Let us begin by identifying your precise location, exactly where you are. Visualize the empty space in front of you. Sense the space of emptiness in front of you, surrounding you. Hold attention on the empty space in front of you. Visualize the empty space in front of you. Mind on emptiness. Look at the empty space. sense the emptiness Allow the emptiness to move close to your face, to your chest. sense the presence of emptiness face the empty space in front of you You and the emptiness. Continue to meditate. on emptiness. Watch, witness, the presence of emptiness. in front of you. Relax your lower jaw, slightly open your mouth, and allow emptiness. Emptiness to enter onto your mouth, then to your throat, emptiness entering further Down through the throat, towards your chest, emptiness, entering inside your chest, creating Taking the empty space, your throat, your chest. The empty space expanding through your lungs, to your solar plexus, expanding emptiness The empty space in your stomach, the emptiness of your body, down to your belly, creating the empty space in your lower belly. Sense the emptiness in your lower belly. in your stomach and abdominal area. Emptiness in your chest. Empty space inside your chest. in your throat, the emptiness rising to the center of your head, emptiness touching your your eyes, your ears, touching on the top of your head, from the inside, the empty space from the belly, through the abdomen, empty in the chest, threat in your head. Emptiness coming out through your ears. Connecting with the emptiness outside of you. The empty space inside you, outside of you You are Empty. Thank you. Your emptiness. in us... There is only emptiness Empty inside, outside, empty in the lower belly. the stomach and the chest and the throat and the head, you are empty. Have a good night everybody.  to within without There is nothing but emptiness. These are very emotional. Make an exhale there, and release. Allow the body to breathe freely and feel the movement of the air. Observe the movement of the air. Follow the gentle movement of air. Thank you. This is the end of the emptiness, practice. Thank you.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 2.9200000000000004, "end": 7.56, "text": " Welcome to the practice of emptiness.", "tokens": [50364, 4027, 281, 264, 3124, 295, 41993, 13, 50997], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16472323187466326, "compression_ratio": 1.25, "no_speech_prob": 0.1002185195684433, "words": [{"word": " Welcome", "start": 2.9200000000000004, "end": 4.32, "probability": 0.902641236782074}, {"word": " to", "start": 4.32, "end": 4.6, "probability": 0.9956075549125671}, {"word": " the", "start": 4.6, "end": 4.76, "probability": 0.9927124977111816}, {"word": " practice", "start": 4.76, "end": 5.14, "probability": 0.9828683137893677}, {"word": " of", "start": 5.14, "end": 6.1, "probability": 0.9942751526832581}, {"word": " emptiness.", "start": 6.1, "end": 7.56, "probability": 0.9379830956459045}]}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 12.66, "end": 28.32, "text": " In the previous sessions of meditation training we have worked with the breathing body, following", "tokens": [50997, 682, 264, 3894, 11081, 295, 12537, 3097, 321, 362, 2732, 365, 264, 9570, 1772, 11, 3480, 51784], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16472323187466326, "compression_ratio": 1.25, "no_speech_prob": 0.1002185195684433, "words": [{"word": " In", "start": 12.0, "end": 12.7, "probability": 0.9704536199569702}, {"word": " the", "start": 12.7, "